{"tid":1934544,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"真的超好聽！Apink鄭恩地演唱Red Velvet的《Psycho》 讓網友表示：「唱功好棒，還笑著唱高音！」","createTime":"2020-03-20T04:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T08:27:12.000Z","uid":16659,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"174f27f4bd7143f7f0442c1898af6094d5efde66","tid":1934544,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:13:21.000Z","msg":"Apink鄭恩地日前透過IG直播和粉絲們互動。<br />\n<br />\n當天她也演唱Red Velvet的《Psycho》，更提到：「澀琪的聲音很棒，最近很喜歡這一首歌，經常會聽尤其是在開車的時候。」而鄭恩地也一個人演唱了全曲。<br />\n<br />\n這段影片在網路上引發不少討論，不少網友更表示：「聲音真的好好聽」、「笑著唱高音的恩地」、「唱功好棒」、「聲音真的很有穿透力」等等。鄭恩地常會通過直播中「唱歌」和粉絲們互動，也曾演唱過中文歌《小幸運》呢！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DOJ9EyfPyiw&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDOJ9EyfPyiw%26feature%3Demb_title&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=e0ee3417\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DOJ9EyfPyiw&amp;feature=emb_title</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，日前Play M娛樂透露：「Apink目前正在準備新專輯，目標是於4月時回歸。」在去年回歸透過主打歌《%%》再度挑戰了新風格的她們，這次會帶著什麼風格回歸，也備受關注呢！"},{"pid":"3a865f54020769421840f450746d176ae527dad7","tid":1934544,"uid":152432,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:21:01.000Z","msg":"Apink依家仲紅唔紅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6356ef7dee71fc20cf0b9706f1456b44438c9fdd","tid":1934544,"uid":96704,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:23:00.000Z","msg":"恩地個樣做乜怪咗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前明明笑得好靚"},{"pid":"c5bc0013c375793c90f5f02d42cc2f81bcf69b87","tid":1934544,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a865f54020769421840f450746d176ae527dad7","tid":1934544,"uid":152432,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T04:21:01.000Z","msg":"Apink依家仲紅唔紅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/do